      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition. It is currently operational and drives, but it shows significant signs of wear both inside and out. There are noticeable scratches and small dents on the exterior, and the interior upholstery exhibits visible staining and wear. All major mechanical systems are functioning, though the car may require maintenance in the near future.",
