    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in 'as-is' condition and will require significant work to be roadworthy again. The engine currently has a noticeable knock and the transmission slips when shifting into higher gears. Visually, the car shows its age with heavy rust on the rocker panels, a cracked windshield, and significant tearing in the upholstery. It would be an ideal candidate for a parts car or a dedicated mechanic looking for a major restoration project.",
